"title": "8435: giving, of oneself",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8435",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The submission of the self to the will of God, in thanksgiving and service.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's self-giving as an example to believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16\">1JN 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:45\">MRK 10:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:13\">JHN 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:3\">ROM 15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:4\">GAL 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1-Eph5:2\">EPH 5:1–5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5-Phil2:8\">PHP 2:5–2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:14\">TIT 2:14</a></p>\n<h2>Why self-giving is reasonable service to God</h2>\n<h3>God's people belong to him by creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:6\">DEU 32:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:3\">PSA 100:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:11\">REV 4:11</a></p>\n<h3>God's people belong to him by redemption</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19-1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:19–6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:9\">REV 5:9</a></p>\n<h3>All good things are given by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:14\">1CH 29:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:18\">DEU 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:25\">ACT 17:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:7\">1CO 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></p>\n<h2>God's people giving themselves</h2>\n<h3>To God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:5\">2CO 8:5</a></p>\n<h3>To one another</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:5\">2CO 8:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:15\">1CO 16:15</a></p>\n<h3>To holy living</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:19\">ROM 6:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:26\">PRO 23:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a></p>\n<h3>To the service of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:58\">1CO 15:58</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:2\">JDG 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:5\">1CH 29:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:16\">2CH 17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:7-Ps40:8\">PSA 40:7–40:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:8\">ISA 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:4\">ACT 6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:9\">ROM 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:15\">1TI 4:15</a></p>\n<h3>To a life of self-denial</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:33\">LUK 14:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:26\">LUK 14:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:2\">ROM 15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:13\">1CO 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:33\">1CO 10:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:15\">2CO 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:8\">PHP 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>To martyrdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:28\">DAN 3:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:24\">ACT 20:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:13\">ACT 21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:11\">REV 12:11</a></p>\n<h2>Rewards of self-giving</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:39\">MAT 10:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:27-Matt19:29\">MAT 19:27–19:29</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:28-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:28–10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:28-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:28–18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:35\">MRK 8:35</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:33\">LUK 17:33</a></p>\n<h2>The giving of thanks</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:23\">PSA 50:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:8\">1CH 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:4\">EPH 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:4-Phil4:7\">PHP 4:4–4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:7\">COL 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:15\">COL 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:28\">HEB 12:28</a></p>",
